                <h1>Travel beyond luxury</h1>
            </div>

        <div class="intro__content cell medium-6 large-5">

                <div class="anim--will-fade-up anim--2000" data-animate>
                    <p><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW212444384 BCX0">Virgin Limited Edition is Sir Richard Branson's collection of unique, luxury retreats located in some of the most breathtaking settings in the world.</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW212444384 BCX0">&nbsp;</span></p>
                </div>

                <div class="buttons-align-left anim--will-fade-up anim--2000" data-animate>
                    <a class="button" href="/our-story/">About us</a>

                    
                </div>
