                                    <a href="/necker-island/"><picture>
                                            <source srcset="/media/nhfnxzs3/necker-island-aerial.jpg?width=640&amp;height=422&amp;quality=70&amp;v=1dc3202938bac40" media="(max-width: 640px)" />
                                            <img src="/media/nhfnxzs3/necker-island-aerial.jpg?width=640&amp;height=555&amp;quality=70&amp;v=1dc3202938bac40" alt="" loading="lazy" />
                                        </picture>
</a>
                                </div>

                            <div class="tabbed-listing__item-content cell medium-6 anim--will-fade-up anim--1500" data-animate>
<a href="/necker-island/"><h2>Necker Island</h2></a>
<h3>British Virgin Islands</h3>
<p><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW199420521 BCX0">Sir Richard Branson's 74-acre world-famous private island in the British Virgin Islands, known for being one of the most idyllic and exclusive places on Earth.</span></p>
                                    <div class="buttons-align-left">
                                        <a class="button" href="/necker-island/">Read more</a>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="tabbed-listing__item tabbed-listing__item--moskito-island grid-x">
                                <div class="tabbed-listing__item-image cell medium-6">
                                    <a href="/the-branson-beach-estate/"><picture>
                                            <source srcset="/media/ctsm3d3l/the-branson-estate-overview.jpg?width=640&amp;height=422&amp;quality=70&amp;v=1db47394a392a90" media="(max-width: 640px)" />
                                            <img src="/media/ctsm3d3l/the-branson-estate-overview.jpg?width=640&amp;height=555&amp;quality=70&amp;v=1db47394a392a90" alt="" loading="lazy" />
                                        </picture>
</a>
                                </div>

                            <div class="tabbed-listing__item-content cell medium-6 anim--will-fade-up anim--1500" data-animate>
<a href="/the-branson-beach-estate/"><h2>The Branson Beach Estate</h2></a>
<h3>British Virgin Islands</h3>
<p>Perched on a dramatic outcrop offering elevated sea views, The Branson Beach Estate at the northeast tip of Moskito Island offers a one-of-a-kind experience in unspoiled seclusion.</p>
                                    <div class="buttons-align-left">
                                        <a class="button" href="/the-branson-beach-estate/">Read more</a>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                </div>
                <div class="tabs-panel" id="europe">
                        <div class="tabbed-listing__item tabbed-listing__item--son-bunyola grid-x">
                                <div class="tabbed-listing__item-image cell medium-6">
                                    <a href="/son-bunyola/"><picture>
                                            <source srcset="/media/r4jbuxk5/son-bunyola-hotel-exterior-pool.jpg?width=640&amp;height=422&amp;quality=70&amp;v=1db473a622615e0" media="(max-width: 640px)" />
                                            <img src="/media/r4jbuxk5/son-bunyola-hotel-exterior-pool.jpg?width=640&amp;height=555&amp;quality=70&amp;v=1db473a622615e0" alt="" loading="lazy" />
                                        </picture>
</a>
                                </div>

                            <div class="tabbed-listing__item-content cell medium-6 anim--will-fade-up anim--1500" data-animate>
<a href="/son-bunyola/"><h2>Son Bunyola</h2></a>
<h3>Mallorca</h3>
<p><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW149133882 BCX0">Son Bunyola is located on the northwest coast of Mallorca. Guests can choose to stay at any of the estate’s three luxury villas and the Son Bunyola Hotel, which opened in June 2023.</span>&nbsp;</p>
                                    <div class="buttons-align-left">
                                        <a class="button" href="/son-bunyola/">Read more</a>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="tabbed-listing__item tabbed-listing__item--the-lodge grid-x">
                                <div class="tabbed-listing__item-image cell medium-6">
                                    <a href="/the-lodge/"><picture>
                                            <source srcset="/media/da4p52a4/the-lodge-exterior-winter.jpg?width=640&amp;height=422&amp;quality=70&amp;v=1dc5e2b4589b690" media="(max-width: 640px)" />
                                            <img src="/media/da4p52a4/the-lodge-exterior-winter.jpg?width=640&amp;height=555&amp;quality=70&amp;v=1dc5e2b4589b690" alt="" loading="lazy" />
                                        </picture>
</a>
                                </div>

                            <div class="tabbed-listing__item-content cell medium-6 anim--will-fade-up anim--1500" data-animate>
<a href="/the-lodge/"><h2>The Lodge</h2></a>
<h3>Verbier, Switzerland</h3>
<p><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW225237331 BCX0">A luxury mountain chalet in Verbier offering world-class skiing in winter and superb hiking, cycling and adventure in summer against a backdrop of Switzerland’s awe-inspiring Alps.</span>&nbsp;</p>
                                    <div class="buttons-align-left">
                                        <a class="button" href="/the-lodge/">Read more</a>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                </div>
                <div class="tabs-panel" id="africa">
                        <div class="tabbed-listing__item tabbed-listing__item--kasbah-tamadot grid-x">
                                <div class="tabbed-listing__item-image cell medium-6">
                                    <a href="/kasbah-tamadot/"><picture>
                                            <source srcset="/media/dybgafzs/kasbah-tamadot-entrance.jpg?width=640&amp;height=422&amp;quality=70&amp;v=1db47399b54de60" media="(max-width: 640px)" />
                                            <img src="/media/dybgafzs/kasbah-tamadot-entrance.jpg?width=640&amp;height=555&amp;quality=70&amp;v=1db47399b54de60" alt="" loading="lazy" />
                                        </picture>
</a>
                                </div>

                            <div class="tabbed-listing__item-content cell medium-6 anim--will-fade-up anim--1500" data-animate>
<a href="/kasbah-tamadot/"><h2>Kasbah Tamadot</h2></a>
<h3>Atlas Mountains, Morocco</h3>
<p><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW189159388 BCX0">A magical Moroccan kasbah nestled in the foothills of the Atlas Mountains, one hour from Marrakech. Stay in authentic Berber tents, luxurious rooms or suites, or one of six Riads.&nbsp;</span></p>
                                    <div class="buttons-align-left">
                                        <a class="button" href="/kasbah-tamadot/">Read more</a>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="tabbed-listing__item tabbed-listing__item--mahali grid-x">
                                <div class="tabbed-listing__item-image cell medium-6">
