                            <div class="tabbed-listing__item-content cell medium-6 anim--will-fade-up anim--1500" data-animate>
<a href="/mont-rochelle/"><h2>Mont Rochelle</h2></a>
<h3>Franschhoek, South Africa</h3>
<p><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW133271187 BCX0">Mont Rochelle is a stunning 26-bedroom hotel and vineyard near Cape Town in the town of Franschhoek in South Africa – an ideal place for rest, relaxation and wine tasting.</span></p>
                                    <div class="buttons-align-left">
                                        <a class="button" href="/mont-rochelle/">Read more</a>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
