                                            <img src="/media/k3lbz2vp/ulusaba-rock-lodge-exterior.jpg?width=640&amp;height=555&amp;quality=70&amp;v=1dc860281295b20" alt="" loading="lazy" />
                                        </picture>
</a>
                                </div>

                            <div class="tabbed-listing__item-content cell medium-6 anim--will-fade-up anim--1500" data-animate>
<a href="/ulusaba/"><h2>Ulusaba</h2></a>
<h3>Sabi Sand Reserve, South Africa</h3>
<p>Reopening in April 2027, Ulusaba in the Sabi Sand Game Reserve is renowned for its exceptional safari experiences, expert rangers and trackers, and distinctive luxury accommodation, now thoughtfully being reimagined for an exciting new chapter.</p>
                                    <div class="buttons-align-left">
                                        <a class="button" href="/ulusaba/">Read more</a>
                                    </div>
