<a href="https://virginhotels.com/" rel="nofollow"><h2>From London to New York: city breaks perfected</h2></a>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Ready to shake up your next city escape? </strong></p>
<p data-start="77" data-end="309">From spontaneous weekends to full-throttle urban adventures, our sister brand Virgin Hotels invites you to experience the city differently. Bold design, smart comforts, and a playful spirit make every stay feel effortless and fun.</p>
<p data-start="311" data-end="511" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Stay in New York, Dallas, Nashville, Las Vegas, New Orleans, Edinburgh, and London, where buzzing spaces, lively rooms, and a stylish social scene make every visit unexpected, and always a good time.</p>
                        <div class="double-image__cta">
                            <a class="button" href="https://virginhotels.com/" rel="nofollow">Explore Virgin Hotels</a>
                        </div>
                </div>
            </div>

